# Python extensions

[![PyPI Version](http://img.shields.io/pypi/v/qwert.svg)](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/qwert/)

Python extensions:

- list-ext
- dict-ext
- file-ext


## Installation

``` console
$ pip3 install qwert
```


## Usage

``` python
from qwert import what-you-need
```
